{"tid":1216383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】史上首次 台灣陸委會發佈「暫避免前往」香港警示","createTime":"2019-06-13T09:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:47:26.000Z","uid":35790,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44e3bc977534d746936c5fbd68b11101c40ac273","tid":1216383,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:57:06.000Z","msg":"【引渡惡法】史上首次 台陸委會發佈「暫避免前往」香港警示<br />\n<br />\n（更新內容）香港政府執意修訂《逃犯條例》，先引發港人周日（9日）103萬人上街抗議，昨日（12日）更發起罷工、罷市、罷課，超過1萬名民眾包圍立法會大樓和政府總部等，遭警方武力驅趕。陸委會今日首次向香港發出「暫避免前往」的旅遊警示。台灣的觀光局表示，目前台灣到香港旅遊的主要是自由行旅客，如果旅客認為有客觀風險，要求取消機票酒店套餐，旅行社可扣除必要費用和5%補償金。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n陸委會指出，香港數以萬計民眾參與昨日抗議《逃犯條例》示威活動，遭暴力驅趕爆發嚴重流血衝突，導致逾70位市民受傷。</span>香港立法會、港府總部周邊地區仍有群眾聚集，部份地鐵站交通運輸受到影響，後續示威活動將有可能再次發生。陸委會提醒近期計劃前往香港的台灣民眾，注意個人安全，勿前往相關地點，並隨時留意交通資訊及事態發展，以免影響行程及安全。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會指出，香港發生民眾抗議示威活動，爆發嚴重流血衝突，提醒台灣民眾要注意旅遊安全，或暫時避免前往。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果台灣民眾在香港旅遊，或台商、台灣鄉親在港遭遇問題，可即時致電香港辦事處急難救助電話（61439012），辦事處將提供相關協助。</span><br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"dc9feed45320c0d3abc3f88e2cbeca3e791a48bd","tid":1216383,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24f4837430afa730601e5a9b9dd40cc8b519d0c","tid":1216383,"uid":39527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:07:46.000Z","msg":"支持其他國家一齊發旅遊警示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347dc824e76a152102589b4c7e67b970636f76db","tid":1216383,"uid":143192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26889cff688bc99ea0bc6f14f7fe45dd74245ca1","tid":1216383,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"即係叫台灣人唔好來香港玩"},{"pid":"72a3164099ca94cddc078b879543cb56c671664c","tid":1216383,"uid":24707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"好波！"},{"pid":"3b44dd1f3fde6e91da294e1e941b3fd0534b4443","tid":1216383,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"支持所有外國撤資香港"},{"pid":"e010fcc18e3a6d58d26b0a0f121f6fa9fbf58dd2","tid":1216383,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:16:52.000Z","msg":"有班反聯合國人類罪嘅蓄生緊係要避免前往啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=0a10bd01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a> <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=488284b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a> <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=0e438c46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=759cd6cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a> <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=63496429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a> <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=3820c23f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議歐美向對示威者施過度武力嘅警察懲處！終生不得踏入歐美國家半步！呢班人渣注定世世代代共享中國人嘅榮耀</span></span>"},{"pid":"8c18dc9926f16d3d041673a8c017675a79773880","tid":1216383,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642546178f4bf0fcedd77f894c29495cd404311f","tid":1216383,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}